    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>Y68.25 (mss. 40 88 400 410 (sec. m. marg.) 2005 2007 2010 2030 2040 2101 2102 2104 2106 4000 4010 4020 4025 4060 4161 4162 5020, 4056):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>āpō</em> abar āb nihišn <em>at̰</em> andar rāh <em>yazamaide</em> pad war ī zōhrag</ab>   
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "At <em>āpō</em>, he has to put it on the water. At <em>at̰</em>, (he has to be) on the way. At yazamaide, (he has to put it) next to the <em>zōhrag</em>."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
        <Quotations id="ritualQuotations">
            <ab>Cf. for the Āb-zōhr with Drōn Yašt N53.31c (cf. <bibl>Kotwal and Kreyenbroek,
                2003</bibl>: pp. 256-7)</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>āpō</em> abar ābat̰ andar rāh-ē <em>ẏazamaide</em> pad war ī zōhrag abāz ōh rēzišn
            </ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "At <em>āpō</em> (he has to put it) over the water. At <em>at̰</em>, on the way. At <em>yazamaide</em> he has to pour it out again next to the <em>zōhrag</em>."</ab>
        </Quotations>
    </Ritual>
